Tight integration for Intel MPI was tested with version
Intel(R) MPI Library for Linux* OS, Version 4.0 Update 3 Build 20110824
Copyright (C) 2003-2011, Intel Corporation. All rights reserved.

Installation of Intel MPI
=========================
Download Intel MPI packages from http://software.intel.com/en-us/articles/intel-mpi-library/
and follow the installation instructions.

Grid Engine tight integration is builtin.

Installing the PE
=================
qconf -Ap $SGE_ROOT/mpi/impi/impi.template

